---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="QR Payment Services - SkanPay"
  description="Review the practical SkanPay service areas around QR checkout readiness, coupon or voucher redemption, merchant confirmation, and partner integration planning."
  activePath="/services/"
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Services</p>
    <h1>QR checkout readiness, kept practical</h1>
    <p>SkanPay service conversations focus on the checkout request, redemption path, customer approval, and merchant-facing result.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="grid two">
      <article class="card route-card">
        <span>01</span>
        <h3>Merchant checkout mapping</h3>
        <p>Define what staff see before scan, during approval, and after the request resolves.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card route-card">
        <span>02</span>
        <h3>QR request structure</h3>
        <p>Clarify the session details a QR request needs to carry for a checkout handoff.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card route-card">
        <span>03</span>
        <h3>Status and timeout behavior</h3>
        <p>Plan how pending, approved, cancelled, expired, and completed states should be handled.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card route-card">
        <span>04</span>
        <h3>Partner app participation</h3>
        <p>Identify where a wallet, payment app, loyalty app, or commerce app fits into the flow.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card route-card">
        <span>05</span>
        <h3>Coupon and voucher coordination</h3>
        <p>Map where offers are validated, how they affect checkout, and what result the merchant receives.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card route-card">
        <span>06</span>
        <h3>Existing processor alignment</h3>
        <p>Frame SkanPay as a gateway layer that can fit around existing processor, acquirer, and POS relationships.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-band">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Next step</p>
      <h2>Use the Technology page for the technical model.</h2>
      <p>For a specific merchant or partner use case, contact SkanPay directly.</p>
    </div>
    <a class="button secondary" href="/qr-payments/">View Technology</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
